Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:03.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.81,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,from loving...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:14.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want things to work with\NMinorin, but it still hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:33.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- U-Um...\N- S-Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:33.80,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Career Planning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was half asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:38.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, it's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:45.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been quite traumatic to have\Nyour buddy Aisaka-san get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:46.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've awakened\Nfrom your nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:55.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,don't forget to turn that in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll repeat this for everyone else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to bring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:02.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NEvery time I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:13.05,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE nijuu yojikan zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nfor 24 hours straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.55,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE kimino koto omoutabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NIt only makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.10,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE modokashii kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nthat much more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:24.06,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE tada afure kaetteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:30.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so simple just to say I love you.\NBut when you come close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:30.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukito ieba kantan nanoni\Nkimiga maeni kichauto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:37.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,my own emotions go awry\Nand get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:37.99,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyaraga sobie watashino\Nkoto wo jamashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:45.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring myself to do anything.\NThat's who I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:45.62,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumonaraba tsuyoki de ikeru\Nsonna seikakunanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:51.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't break this\Nwall down no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:51.88,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna ganbatte mitemo kabewa kuzusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:55.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand these feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:55.46,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sasshite hoshii kono kimoch iwo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these gazes of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,dakara watashi wa itsumo kimini
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.68,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,daisuki dayoto okuru shisen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather up my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:06.60,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,saidaino yuukide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile heart made of silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.15,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yabure souna shirukuno haato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:13.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that by meeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:13.69,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimini atte kizuita yatto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:19.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:19.41,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,ainiwa bukiyou dattan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A forgotten scar left in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.12,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,wasure kaketa koino kizuato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I suddenly felt it sting deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.71,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuuni uzuki dashitano kyunto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:32.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that I love you someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:32.17,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsukawa watashi rashiku sukito iwanakya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:37.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll keep making me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:37.01,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,imayori yowaku nacchauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:44.88,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,When You're Around
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:47.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, we suffered only minor injuries\Nwhen the search team rescued us,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:51.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Taiga's mom came to the\Nlodge to pick her up after that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been in touch with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:01.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach said that Aisaka isn't doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's apparently staying with\Nher parents to recuperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:06.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach her cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to act like you were the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,...who saved Taiga that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If Taiga asks, say it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:32.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Say she was unconscious the whole\Ntime and never said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:39.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this related to the wish Aisaka\Nasked me to grant on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:42.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go somewhere fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop dwelling on Tiger—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.97,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Realms of Desire\NRamen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freaking freezing! The group\Nahead of us is taking forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, do you still need to make dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:19.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'm already here. I can't\Nleave before trying the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go home\Neven when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought of talking about\Ncareer plans with my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak out about it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This round is only for dividing\Nup next year's classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto-chi, you'll be in liberal arts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:35.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan's to major in literature somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,become editor of a music magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually go freelance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:42.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I just wanna graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:49.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll probably end up\Nworking for my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:55.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Guess I shouldn't be surprised that\Nyou're all thinking about your futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice to be a genius\Nwithout a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going into the sciences, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Professor Kitamura will have\Nno trouble on the national tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'm going to college...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Next person in line please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! We're finally up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Find a place to squeeze\Nyourself in nice and tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You keeping tabs on anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- She's probably—\N- Liberal arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-Kushieda!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Days are shorter in the winter,\Nso we get out early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now give me your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I should mention that I'll poke your eyes\Nout if you ask for a long noodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Long noodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:47.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Three orders of regular ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excellent choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Three orders of ramen!\N- You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You started another new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The pay's good, so I'm trying\Nit out for a couple hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always working?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to open his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Art of Endless Transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.99,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Realms of Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:40.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl never changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:47.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Never would've guessed she just rejected\Nsomeone, if you hadn't told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:52.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are impossible to predict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, did you make up\Nwith Little Miss Maya, Noto-chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, she's completely ignoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl's feelings, huh...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:17.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is her health really what's keeping her away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:24.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is her mom selfish like her dad,\Nrefusing to let her come back?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is it...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stop myself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:34.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she realize I heard what she said...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...from loving...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Career plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:47.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put, "I'm going to study hard."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get into a national university\Nclose to home, it'll cost way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:57.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Natto bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh! Sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're smart, unlike me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have the best education!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And make the most of your talents!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:19.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And live a super happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:29.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Polish the crown jewels...and the\Ncrown jewels will shine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A jewel must be polished\Nbefore it can shine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:39.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You shine so brightly when you're studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:44.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had a job, even 50,000 yen a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you say now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:53.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The one time you worked at Inage-san's\Nplace was an exceptional exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:59.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have time to study\Nif you're working, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we have to eat dinner cold, separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll no longer have a reason to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't be happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only saying all this because\Nyou want me to go to college!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's always been like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Growing up without a daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}doesn't mean you'll be less happy than the other kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'm a super mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:36.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be completely happy, forever and ever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:48.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Completely happy, forever and ever, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga's fine, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:10.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she and her mom get along fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:15.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're catching up on stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you need our budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn it in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Please do, new team captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, our new president is very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the new team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't you already captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:43.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But since Kitamura-kun's so busy\Nwith the student council,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,we combined the boys' and girls' ball teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was appointed captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:55.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, woe am I for becoming\Nas busy as Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:59.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then why did you start a new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't that make it worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:05.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to seek hardships\Nwhile you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll end up doing worse at both...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working hard to keep\Nthat from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Hi, Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' lovely today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:24.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the attitude, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidity is contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess when the kid's away, daddy will play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Kawashima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I must depart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Adieu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:45.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Skipping first period?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been\Nwanting to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Still got something left after\Nall that screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The crack you're sitting in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,home to a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That space between the\Nvending machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,is where a heartbroken girl choked\Non a bottle of soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me sooner!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing bad's happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe ghosts have their\Nown personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:47.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They show themselves only to the people\Nwho they believe understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:52.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I once thought...that I'd found a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:58.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get so caught up\Nin searching for what I can't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,that I lose sight of what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care enough to hear you finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd just hear me\Nout, you'd understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I had just stood by and watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't brought anything to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've all gone perfectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to you makes me\Nfeel like I'm on my period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is clear now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep my head on straight\Nand focus on what I can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. Zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my own decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:34.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, about your career plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't finish talking\Nit over with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:53.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you haven't changed your mind\Nfrom the beginning of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:59.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an excellent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:02.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That gives me certain expectations,\Nwhich drives me to sound like a nag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't waste your time on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My family's poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's because of finances?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing, there are\Nscholarships, student loans—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so strange to not\Nwant to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what your career plan tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:29.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how {\i1}you{\i0} feel—no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How I feel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's pitch dark in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:50.16,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,New part-time job! I'll be going straight\Nto the bar from there.   -Yasuko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:57.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is what she meant when she\Nsaid everything will work out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't she also say that life has\Nno meaning if we can't eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:08.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shine so brightly when you're studying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:15.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too late to give this to her now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's so embarrassing about a love letter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well? Are you weirded out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:43.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I don't have the guts to tell her\Nhow I feel, all I can do is fantasize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pathetic, sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't feel any shame!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:52.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to feel ashamed\Nabout being in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't say that when\Nshe's in love with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, I couldn't tell her if I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't answer her phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:04.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:05.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you working a new...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:16.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-Ta-Ta-Ta—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been!? Who were\Nyou with!? What were you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pig! Dog! Yaksha lookalike!\NAsura face! Skullduggery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:33.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,First you try to strangle me,\Nnow you're giving me funny looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You surprised me, showing up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You never called or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was r-really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the battery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not come back because you're in—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What was I about to say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:07.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't hurt that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lying about not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I hadn't seen Mommy in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:25.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed at a hotel together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:28.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Went shopping, ate out, watched movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I let her spoil me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you weren't going\Nto come over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:42.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enter my room\Nthrough your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the three-second rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you make it through\Nin three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:49.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:54.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, since you're here,\Nwhy not stay for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some leftover natto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I could add green onions\Nand make an omelet—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No need. I already ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah! Inko-chan wants to say hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sound asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Playing dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new trick she learned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Fugly put on weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She did, huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:21.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because you're\Nnot around to stress her—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gorging herself out of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still fugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Boing, boing. Boing, boing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:37.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having Taiga next to me just feels...right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryu—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying? That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It is pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Fugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:08.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had some free time,\Nso I was cleaning up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole mess makes that painfully clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:16.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:20.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still trying to do the best I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:27.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, were you able to find\Nout how Minorin really feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:34.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you miss your chance to ask her\Nbecause of the trouble I caused?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}Why are you worrying about me?{\i0}\N- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- {\i1}I mean...{\i0}\N- I won't screw up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:40.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you and Minorin\Nwill work things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!\NGive me a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:06.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I always forget to lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:18.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for your apartment's\Nairtight security.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:35.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You went with Kitamura-kun and\NMinorin to look for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:41.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't remember,\Nsince you were unconscious and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun was carrying me on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:54.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I started babbling silly\Nthings in my haze...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was just a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Silly things, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:10.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She wants to pretend it never happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:11.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:20.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura did carry you\Nup the cliff on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:21.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say a word, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You were unconscious the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:33.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I was freaking\Nout that it actually happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:39.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:48.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:53.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,In those sleepless nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:13.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nemurenai yoruni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:16.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I lay there sighing all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:16.27,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hitoride tameiki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.86,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,minna wa dounano
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:23.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It just feels so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:23.65,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nandaka samishii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:30.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiny little seed in this huge Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:30.12,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,hiroi daichini hitotsubu no tane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:33.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch out those roots,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:33.41,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nekko nobashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:41.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and bear a fruit that's still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:41.04,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,mada aoi miwo tsuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:45.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The fruit that wants to hurry and turn orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:45.92,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji ironi hayaku naritai kajitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:49.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Showering in your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:49.22,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimino hikari wo abite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,only nurtures bigger ideals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.72,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,risou ya yume wa fukuramu bakari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.10,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kizuiteyo nee
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:03.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the orange today but cried\Nbecause it was still too sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:03.02,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji kyoumo tabete mitakedo\Nmada suppakute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:06.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded too much of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:06.49,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi mitaide nokosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finished the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.49,0:23:08.90,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,zenbu tabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. It makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo nakeruyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:22.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:22.33,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo sukidayo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:35.01,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Path to Take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, Paper, Scissors\Nfor thirtysomethings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:29.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee! I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:30.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.47,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,C-H-O-C-O-L-A-T-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:35.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine's Day is so much fun!
